第01课：终结“封建”制度的大秦帝国

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appcU2ejZM69413/a_5be3a91429101_B49KtsvJ

<section style="white-space: normal; padding: 1rem 0px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0.8rem solid rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;"><section style="padding: 1rem 0px 2rem; margin: 0px 2rem 1rem; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(244, 244, 244);"><span style="font-size: 20px;">老师简介</span></section><section style="padding: 2.4rem 0px 0.5rem; margin: 0px; text-align: center;"><section style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; width: 7.5rem; height: 7.5rem; border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden;"><img title=".jpg" alt="老师头像.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/86680500_1547878592.jpg"/></section><section style="padding: 0.8rem 0px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); font-weight: 600;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">梅毅</span></section><section style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); line-height: 1.72;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">《百家讲坛》主讲人、引领中国历史出版物热潮</span><br/></section></section><section style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 2rem 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.72;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">梅毅，《百家讲坛》主讲人，国家一级作家。推波中国历史出版热潮。<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">《百家讲坛》以他的名字开辟新系列——“梅毅话英雄”。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">他以敢于坐冷板凳的执着精神，<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">独立完成了10卷本、500多万字</strong>的《中华英雄史》系列丛书。也因此，他以笔名“<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">赫连勃勃大王</strong>”引领出版界，被誉为“中国互联网<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">历史写作第一人</strong>”。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">他还是多档文化精品节目的坐上宾，与窦文涛、金运昌、纪文海等众文化名嘴对谈古今，博弈众彩。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">此次，梅毅<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">首次网络独家献声</strong>，认真打磨<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">《梅毅带你读懂中国史·第一季》</strong>。表层史实下的底层人性、沿袭至今的处事之道，以及看待问题的大智慧与大格局，梅毅将通过56讲为你一一道来</span>。</p></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p></p><section style="white-space: normal; padding: 1rem 0px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;"><section style="padding: 1rem 0px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none;"><section style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 2rem 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.72;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/9699800_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">说到与我们中国人<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">最仰望的伟大时代</strong>，强秦盛汉，肯定要算。它和当今世界有得一比，是一个人才辈出，人人都有机会扬名立万的时代。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">·李斯，小公务员一跃成当朝丞相；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">·韩信，淮阴街头小青年奋斗成大元帅；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">·刘邦，副股级的泗水亭长，后来居上成正国级大汉朝开国皇帝……</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">论<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">英雄奇士</strong>，只秦汉两代就灿若群星；论<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">文化集大成者</strong>，中国的诸子百家早早领先于世界；论<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">处事格局</strong>，中国古代史堪称一部人间处世修炼教科书。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/27648600_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">· 大格局历史观和独一无二的大智慧</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">活在当下，只有通晓历史，才会有真正的格局；只有了解了华夏民族文化变迁，才能获得大智慧。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">· 物质时代的精神疗愈</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">浮躁和“成功学”至上的当下，没有坚定的信念很容易让人随波逐流。学历史就是让我们找到那颗精神支柱，治愈蝇营狗苟的精神瘫痪。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">· 经得起时间检验的美学观</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">真实历史中的美远胜你看过的任何历史剧。梅老师通过美的表达和叙述，为你还原一个个真实的历史现场。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">· 突破职场与生活瓶颈的内驱力</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">一个人要想在工作和生活中有所成绩，知识，经历，阅历，见解，都非常关键。以人为鉴，以史为鉴，我们才能从历史中看到未来。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/45723800_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">1.&nbsp;告别死板教科书，趣味学历史</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">梅老师将用<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">现场感的讲述</strong>还原历史事件，从<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">人性的角度</strong>解读有血有肉的历史人物，让学历史成为像听相声一样轻松有趣的事。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">2.&nbsp;你从没听过的新知和独家史料</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">五花八门的网络历史爆料，甚至是历史畅销水书都无法给你真正的历史。梅老师以<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">正史为主线，夹杂天马行空的杂史</strong>，带给你只有从古书里才能获得的新知，和频频<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">颠覆认知的真实史料</strong>。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">56节评书式</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">历史课，<strong>20年研究</strong>的心血灌注之作。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">还原<strong>有趣有料</strong>的历史现场，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">有血有肉</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">的英雄奇士，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">百度、知乎学不到的<strong>独家史料</strong>，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">带给你独一无二的<strong>大智慧和大格局历史观</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/72002800_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/98428200_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img title="undefined" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" alt="undefined" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/29795900_1547878594.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img title="undefined" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" alt="undefined" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/52111900_1547878594.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/74997000_1547878594.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(250, 192, 143); letter-spacing: 0px;">▌购买须知</span></strong><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(250, 192, 143); letter-spacing: 0px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;">课程原价</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-decoration-line: line-through; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px;">199元</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;">，预售价格</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(250, 192, 143); letter-spacing: 0px;">99</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;">元。本课程为虚拟产品，订阅成功后，暂不支持退订、转让，望您理解。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;"><br/></span></p>