n></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">梅老师将用<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">现场感的讲述</strong>还原历史事件，从<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">人性的角度</strong>解读有血有肉的历史人物，让学历史成为像听相声一样轻松有趣的事。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">2.&nbsp;你从没听过的新知和独家史料</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">五花八门的网络历史爆料，甚至是历史畅销水书都无法给你真正的历史。梅老师以<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">正史为主线，夹杂天马行空的杂史</strong>，带给你只有从古书里才能获得的新知，和频频<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">颠覆认知的真实史料</strong>。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">56节评书式</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">历史课，<strong>20年研究</strong>的心血灌注之作。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">还原<strong>有趣有料</strong>的历史现场，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">有血有肉</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">的英雄奇士，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">百度、知乎学不到的<strong>独家史料</strong>，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">带给你独一无二的<strong>大智慧和大格局历史观</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/72002800_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/98428200_1547878593.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img title="undefined" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" alt="undefined" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/29795900_1547878594.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img title="undefined" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" alt="undefined" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/52111900_1547878594.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><img style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: block;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9He58bHl9078/image/ueditor/74997000_1547878594.jpg%25252540%25252521w1080"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(250, 192, 143); letter-spacing: 0px;">▌购买须知</span></strong><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(250, 192, 143); letter-spacing: 0px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 1rem 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;">课程原价</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-decoration-line: line-through; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px;">199元</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;">，预售价格</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(250, 192, 143); letter-spacing: 0px;">99</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;">元。本课程为虚拟产品，订阅成功后，暂不支持退订、转让，望您理解。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); letter-spacing: 0px;"><br/></span></p>